  "text": "Challenge one: relating food-web structure to ecosystem function There is now an established suite of attributes that describe food-web structure, and it is known that food-web structure can influence function [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The central challenge is determining which aspects of structure are related to which aspects of function. Because many food-web attributes systematically vary with the size and complexity of webs (Box 1, [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] ) understanding these underlying patterns is critical in determining relationships between attributes and ecosystem functions.",
